@startuml finding-state
!theme plain
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #0277BD
}

[*] --> Draft : new finding
Draft --> Sent : notify owner
Sent --> InReview : owner opens
InReview --> Accept : approved
InReview --> Reject : declined
InReview --> Clarify : needs info
InReview --> Route : wrong owner
InReview --> Escalate : above review level
InReview --> OutOfScope : outside boundary
InReview --> Defer : cannot act now
Clarify --> InReview : info provided
Route --> Sent : re-assigned
Defer --> Sent : deferral expires
Escalate --> Resolved : escalation handled
OutOfScope --> Closed : documented

Accept --> Resolved : action completed
Reject --> Closed : reason logged
Resolved --> [*]
Closed --> [*]

note bottom
  States ensure audit trail
  and change control
end note

@enduml
